  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large mortar, pound the parsley, garlic, and a pinch of salt until well combined.",
    "In a large Dutch oven, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion, carrots, and potatoes, and cook until the vegetables are tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Add the lamb, tomato paste, beef broth, salt, and pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Cover the Dutch oven with a lid, and transfer it to the preheated oven.",
    "Bake for 2 1/2 hours, or until the lamb is tender and the vegetables are cooked through.",
    "Stir in the parsley mixture, and serve hot.",
    "Let the casserole rest for 10 minutes before serving."
  ],
